{"word":"G5119 - τότε - tóte - tot'-eh - That time","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τότε</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">tóte</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tot'-eh</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">That time</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அப்பொழுது, அதுமுதல், ஆகிலும் - ஒப்புமை வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"then; at that time"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From (the neuter of) <a href=\"#/G3588 - ὁ - ho - ho/3588\">G3588</a> and <a href=\"#/G3753 - ὅτε - hóte - hot'-eh/3753\">G3753</a>; <i>the when</i>, that is, <i>at the time</i> that (of the past or future, also in consecution): - that time, then.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}